{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"terminology\"><a href=\"#terminology\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Terminology</h2>\n<p><strong>Property</strong> (red) and <strong>value</strong> (blue)</p>\n<pre><code>p { <span style=\"color: red\">font-weight:</span> <span style=\"color: blue\">bold;</span> }\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Declaration</strong> (red)</p>\n<p>A single property-value pair</p>\n<pre><code>p { <span style=\"color: red\">font-weight: bold;</span> }\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Selector</strong> – shown in red <strong>Declaration block</strong> – shown in blue</p>\n<p>Includes ALL of the individual declarations</p>\n<pre><code><span style=\"color: red\">p</span> <span style=\"color: blue\">{ font-weight: bold;\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"ways-to-include-css-in-your-document\"><a href=\"#ways-to-include-css-in-your-document\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Ways to include CSS in your document</h2>\n<p><strong>External stylesheet</strong> : attach a separate document in the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head&gt;</code> of your HTML.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;link href=&quot;css/styles.css&quot; rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; /&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Internal stylesheet</strong> or <strong>embedded stylesheet</strong> : Include styles in the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;style&gt;</code> tag in the <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head&gt;</code> of your HTML</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;style&gt;\n    body {\n        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n    }\n&lt;/style&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>Inline styles</strong> : occur in the HTML tag itself</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token style-attr language-css\"><span class=\"token attr-name\"> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=\"</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> purple<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>I am a purple paragraph!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"which-should-you-use\"><a href=\"#which-should-you-use\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Which should you use?</h2>\n<p>99.999% of the time: External stylesheet</p>\n<p>It is rare that you will need inline or embedded/internal styles, but you should know they are possible.</p>\n<h2 id=\"css-selectors\"><a href=\"#css-selectors\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS Selectors</h2>\n<p>We will cover four simple ways to include CSS in your document:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Elements: HTML tags as selectors</li>\n<li>Classes</li>\n<li>IDs</li>\n<li>Descendant selector</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"element-selectors\"><a href=\"#element-selectors\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Element selectors</h3>\n<p>Simply list the HTML tag and how you'd like it styled.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">body {\n    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"class-selectors-classname\"><a href=\"#class-selectors-classname\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Class selectors <code class=\"language-text\">.classname</code></h3>\n<p>Create a class and attach it to an HTML tag to make the class appear.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You may have more than one class per tag.</li>\n<li>You may use a class several times in a document.</li>\n<li>Classes are more specific than HTML elements and will generally override them.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style language-css\">\n<span class=\"token selector\">.warning</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> orange<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bold<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>warning<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>This paragraph displays a warning!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"id-selectors-idname\"><a href=\"#id-selectors-idname\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ID selectors <code class=\"language-text\">#idname</code></h3>\n<p>Create an ID and attach it to an HTML tag to make the styling appear.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You may use the ID only once per page.</li>\n<li>Each element may have only one ID.</li>\n<li>IDs are the most specific, overriding styles from elements and classes.</li>\n<li>IDs are not commonly used in CSS these days. They are more commonly used with JavaScript.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style language-css\">\n<span class=\"token selector\">#danger</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bold<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">text-transform</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> uppercase<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>danger<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>This text is uppercase, bold, and red, and you better pay attention because you're in danger only once on this web page!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"descendant-selectors-classname-element-\"><a href=\"#descendant-selectors-classname-element-\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Descendant selectors <code class=\"language-text\">.classname element {}</code></h3>\n<p>This is a combination of one or more classes, IDs, or elements, separated by spaces, to indicate a family relationship.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style language-css\">\n<span class=\"token selector\">.warning p</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> violet<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>article</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>warning<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>All paragraphs in this article will have a color of violet.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>This paragraph too! No more classes needed!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>article</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"grouping-selectors\"><a href=\"#grouping-selectors\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Grouping selectors</h2>\n<p>Make all <code class=\"language-text\">h1</code> AND <code class=\"language-text\">h2</code> red:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style language-css\">\n<span class=\"token selector\">h4, h5</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> green<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>I'm Green<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>I'm Green Too!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Make only the <code class=\"language-text\">h4</code>'s in <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;section&gt;</code> blue:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style language-css\">\n<span class=\"token selector\">section h6</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>I'm blue!!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>I'm NOT blue<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Make the <code class=\"language-text\">h4</code>'s and <code class=\"language-text\">h5</code>'s inside <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;section&gt;</code> pink:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style language-css\">\n<span class=\"token selector\">section h4, section h5</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pink<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>I'm pink!!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>I'm pink too<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>I'm NOT pink<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>For easier reading, you may wish to write selectors on seperate lines:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">section h4,\nsection h5 {\n    color: pink;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"common-css-properties-and-values\"><a href=\"#common-css-properties-and-values\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Common CSS properties and values</h2>\n<h3 id=\"font-family\"><a href=\"#font-family\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>font-family</h3>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<th>\n Property name\n </th>\n <th>\n Possible values                                                          </th>\n </tr>\n   <tr>\n      <td valign=\"top\"><p></p>\n      </td>\n      <td><p>Establishes the font family/families. Standard choices include:</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><strong>Sans-serif</strong>: Arial, Helvetica, Trebuchet MS, Verdana</li>\n          <li><strong>Serif</strong>: Times, Times New Roman, Georgia</li>\n          <li><strong>Monospace</strong>: Courier</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p><code>font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;</code></p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td valign=\"top\"><p>font-size</p></td>\n      <td><p>Default browser size is 16px = 1em = 1 rem</p>\n        <p><code>font-size: 1rem;</code></p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td valign=\"top\"><p>font-style</p>\n      </td>\n      <td><p>Should the font be italic?</p>\n        <p><code>font-style: italic;</code></p>\n        <p><code>font-style: normal;</code></p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td valign=\"top\"><p>font-weight</p>\n      </td>\n      <td><p>Should the font be bold?</p>\n        <p><code>font-weight: bold;</code></p>\n        <p><code>font-weight: normal;</code></p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td valign=\"top\"><p>font</p></td>\n      <td><p>Shorthand for multiple font properties.</p>\n        <p><code>font: italic bold 1rem/1.3rem  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;</code></p>\n        <p>Font is Arial/Helvetica/sans-serif, italic, and bold, and 1rem in size, with 1.3rem line spacing.</p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td valign=\"top\"><p>line-spacing</p></td>\n      <td><p>Distance between lines.</p>\n        <p><code>line-spacing: 1.3rem;</code></p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td valign=\"top\"><p>color</p></td>\n      <td><p>Text color.</p>\n        <p><code>color: white;</code></p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n   <tr>\n      <td valign=\"top\"><p>background</p>\n        <p>background-color<br/>\n        background-image<br/>\n        background-position<br/>\n        background-repeat</p>\n        </td>\n      <td><p>Dealing with background images and colors. Background property is shorthand for all of the other properties.</p>\n        <p>By default, background images repeat.</p>\n        <p><code>background-color: blue;</code></p>\n        <p><code>background: red url(image.jpg) no-repeat left top;</code></p>\n        <p>means a background color of red, background image of image.jpg, display it once at the left top corner, no repeat of the image.</p>\n        <p>Image will display over the color. You may specify a color in case the image doesn't display.</p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td valign=\"top\"><p>text-decoration</p></td>\n      <td><p>Turns off the underline in links.</p>\n        <p>Values include none, underline.</p>\n        <p><code>text-decoration: none;</code></p>\n   </td>\n    </tr>\n        <tr>\n      <td valign=\"top\"><p>:link<br/>\n        :visited<br/>\n        :focus<br/>\n        :hover<br/>\n        :active</p></td>\n      <td><p>Pseudoclasses: specify styling in these states.</p>\n        <ul>\n          <li>:link -- unvisited link</li>\n          <li>:visited -- visited state</li>\n          <li>:focus -- the currently \"focused\" (selected) element </li>\n          <li>:hover -- hover your mouse over this </li>\n          <li>:active -- the time between the link is selected and the time the page loads. (Not used much today.)</li>\n        </ul>\n        <p>If you are using these pseudoclasses, they MUST go in the order listed.</p>\n        <p>To remember:</p>\n        <p><strong>L</strong>ord <strong>V</strong>ader <strong>F</strong>ormer <strong>H</strong>andle <strong>A</strong>nakin</p>\n        <p>:link, :visited, :active are used almost exclusively on links (the <strong>A</strong> tag).</p>\n        <p>The pseudoclasses :focus and :hover are used with links and with any other element on the page. :focus is especially useful with forms and in accessibility contexts.</p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n </table>\n<h2 id=\"references\"><a href=\"#references\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>References</h2>\n<p><strong>HTML Elements Reference</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element\">https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element</a></p>\n<p><strong>InternetingIsHard.com</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Hello CSS <a href=\"https://internetingishard.com/html-and-css/hello-css/\">https://internetingishard.com/html-and-css/hello-css/</a></li>\n<li>CSS Selectors <a href=\"https://internetingishard.com/html-and-css/css-selectors/\">https://internetingishard.com/html-and-css/css-selectors/</a></li>\n<li>Links and Images <a href=\"https://internetingishard.com/html-and-css/links-and-images/\">https://internetingishard.com/html-and-css/links-and-images/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Validating CSS</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://jigsaw.w3.org/css-validator/\">http://jigsaw.w3.org/css-validator/</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"exercises\"><a href=\"#exercises\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Exercises</h2>\n<h3 id=\"style-your-book-chapter\"><a href=\"#style-your-book-chapter\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Style your book chapter</h3>\n<p>Look at the book chapter that you marked up yesterday.</p>\n<p>To this, add some CSS styling. Make use of:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Colors, background images, styling text</li>\n<li>CSS selectors: elements, classes, ID, descendent selector</li>\n<li>Include styles in an external stylesheet</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"additional-css-practice\"><a href=\"#additional-css-practice\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Additional CSS practice</h2>\n<p>If you finish early, and/or you want some more practice, work through the following sections of exercises at W3Schools:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/html/exercise.asp\">https://www.w3schools.com/html/exercise.asp</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>HTML Styles, all exercises (inline styles only)</li>\n<li>HTML CSS, all exercises (embedded styles)</li>\n<li>HTML Links, exercise 4</li>\n<li>HTML Images, exercise 2</li>\n<li>HTML Classes, all exercises</li>\n<li>HTML IDs, all exercises</li>\n</ul>\n<p>There are additional exercises at this link:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/css/exercise.asp\">https://www.w3schools.com/css/exercise.asp</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>CSS Syntax</li>\n<li>CSS How To</li>\n<li>CSS Background</li>\n<li>CSS Text</li>\n<li>CSS Links</li>\n<li>CSS Fonts</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"on-your-own\"><a href=\"#on-your-own\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>On Your Own</h3>\n<p>Begin styling the \"about\" page you made yesterday.</p>\n<p>If you still need more to do, make a page about some of your hobbies and activities and style it, or style the hobbies page you made yesterday. Include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>What is this hobby exactly?</li>\n<li>How does it make you feel?</li>\n<li>Where have you traveled because of your hobby? What other life experiences has your hobby provided, that you might not otherwise experience?</li>\n<li>Photos and/or videos of your hobby in action</li>\n<li>Links to websites describing your hobby, or where hobbyists discuss what they do</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you manage to get as far as creating both web pages, link them together with a navigation bar.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/css","title":"CSS","order":3}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":0,"path":"/intro","title":"Introduction to the Course"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":1,"path":"/setup","title":"Setup & Prerequisites"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":2,"path":"/html","title":"HTML"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":3,"path":"/css","title":"CSS"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":4,"path":"/programming-fundamentals","title":"Programming Fundamentals"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":5,"path":"/functions-and-scope","title":"Functions and Scope"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":6,"path":"/quiz","title":"Exercise: Quiz"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":7,"path":"/objects-and-arrays","title":"Objects and Arrays"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":8,"path":"/tests","title":"Exercise: Make the Tests Pass"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":9,"path":"/dom","title":"The DOM"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":10,"path":"/calculator","title":"Building an HTML, CSS, and JavaScript Calculator"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":11,"path":"/mole","title":"Exercise: Feed-A-Star-Mole"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":12,"path":"/ajax","title":"AJAX"}}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"order":13,"path":"/dogs","title":"Exercise: Dog App"}}}]}},"pageContext":{}}